data.description: Step inside this inviting home and discover its warmth and character. Picture yourself spending tranquil afternoons gently rocking on the porch swing of your sunroom, creating cherished memories in your own private retreat. This home offers both practicality and charm, featuring a detached garage accessible via the alleyway. With newer flooring and freshly painted interiors, this home truly glows with a welcoming ambiance. As you enter, you're greeted by the inviting living room, complete with a comforting fireplace, perfect for cozy evenings with loved ones. The seamless layout between living spaces ensures effortless entertaining, whether you're hosting a dinner party or simply enjoying a quiet night in. Conveniently located just two blocks from the Parma City Public Swimming Pool, opportunities for recreation & relaxation abound. Whether it's a refreshing swim on a hot summer day or a leisurely stroll around the neighborhood, you'll find endless ways to unwind and enjoy life. Come see your new home today!
